===[[Pokémon Mezastar]]===
Goh, in a version based on the animated series, appeared in [[Pokémon Mezastar]]. In this game, Goh is seen using {{p|Scizor}}, {{p|Grookey}}, {{p|Drizzile}}, and {{p|Cinderace}}. In the [[Super Tag set 1 (Mezastar)|first Super Tag series]], as part of a tie-in with the animated series, [[Ash Ketchum|Ash]], Goh, or the [[Team Rocket trio]] could randomly challenge the player as a Trainer and Battle opponent. Upon beating the character, the player can receive a Support Pokémon Ticket based on [[Goh's Cinderace]], with a tag partner based on [[Goh's Scizor]].

